\begin_layout Standard
Mean
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha\approx[0.15,0.22,0.29,0.34]$
\end_inset
 for 9/12/18/24 h, yet argmax is 24 h in 86% of windows because the
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha_{24}-\alpha_{18}$
\end_inset
