 Nested suffixes through a 
\emph{shared}
 encoder yield nearly identical states (
\begin_inset Formula $h_{18}$
\end_inset
–
\begin_inset Formula $h_{24}$
\end_inset
 cosine 0.984).
 Forcing uniform
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset
 or always-12 h matches learned median FDE (~19.5 km); always-24 h is not better.
 Motion–
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset
 correlations are weak; geography is a stronger soft driver than maneuver features.
 The gate does 
\emph{not}
 implement
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset
maneuver→short / straight→long
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset
.
